Former GFMS Metals Analyst Nikos Kavalis Joins RBS in London

-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 
2011-08-25T10:55:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/former-gfms-metals-analyst-nikos-kavalis-joins-rbs-in-london.html
Nikos Kavalis has joined RBS Global
Banking & Markets in  London  as a metals analyst, said  Nick Moore , chief commodities strategist.  Kavalis started covering base and precious metals for RBS
Global in June and reports to Moore. Prior to that Kavalis
worked at London-based research consultancy  GFMS Ltd.  for eight
years covering precious metals and the copper market.  “Nikos has extensive precious and base metal consulting
experience with GFMS,” Moore said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Agnieszka Troszkiewicz in London at 
 atroszkiewic@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at  ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  